{"name": "Music - Guitar", "id": 236, "content": "<p>Music is composed of Tension &amp; Release. Start somewhere, build tension, slowly release. It&#39;s also about patterns. Pattern of intervals/gaps, pattern of pitch, pattern of leap, pattern of pattern, ...</p>\n\n<p>Musicality also comes from variation: Low and high, slow and fast, Sound and silence, Bright and dark, emotion and dullness, ...</p>\n\n<p>Songs are based on Melody + Ornamentation.</p>\n\n<p>Tool&nbsp;for chord identification:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.oolimo.de/gitarrenakkorde/analysieren\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oolimo.de/gitarrenakkorde/analysieren</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.8notes.com/all/classical/sheet_music/?difficulty=2\" target=\"_blank\">Sheets/Tabs</a></p>\n\n<p>Etudes:</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>Giuliani</td>\n\t\t\t<td>Handel</td>\n\t\t\t<td>Carulli</td>\n\t\t\t<td>Carcassi</td>\n\t\t\t<td>Barrios</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H4efd1j73jY&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yLEe7vOhlm56wR-La9kk9N\" target=\"_blank\">Danza</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9E6xPt5or5Q&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2wb9glEWkllrQivebn5ckhE&amp;index=32\" target=\"_blank\">Am-2</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPxX5OgpPf8&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2xD07bSIbYB093JOYYYcpd-\" target=\"_blank\">Op36-Capriccio</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_qkS6u4VcA&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2xdssom-fC4q9uq83BVEvwg&amp;index=6\" target=\"_blank\">Op10-2</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vw5orUcH5no&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yEr5d3JjfNgMAzKeyN8Kwy\" target=\"_blank\">A Mi Madre</a></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FcpTVySaTzI&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yLEe7vOhlm56wR-La9kk9N&amp;index=8\">Op30-1</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XstVP9kgLks&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2wb9glEWkllrQivebn5ckhE&amp;index=33\" target=\"_blank\">Am-3</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jT7CniOIcAI&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2xD07bSIbYB093JOYYYcpd-&amp;index=3\" target=\"_blank\">Op114-2</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tuukN8ruu3Q&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yEr5d3JjfNgMAzKeyN8Kwy&amp;index=52\" target=\"_blank\">Am</a></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LE85zVghJXI&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yLEe7vOhlm56wR-La9kk9N&amp;index=10\" target=\"_blank\">Op30-3</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YfwHMgq2Fbc&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2wb9glEWkllrQivebn5ckhE&amp;index=34\" target=\"_blank\">Am-4</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KTyJiqwxCK0&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2xD07bSIbYB093JOYYYcpd-&amp;index=4\" target=\"_blank\">Op114-3</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0WikvfLMqKc&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yEr5d3JjfNgMAzKeyN8Kwy&amp;index=53\" target=\"_blank\">Cm</a></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PRtFDvxQUis&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yLEe7vOhlm56wR-La9kk9N&amp;index=16\" target=\"_blank\">Op30-9</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1vP8m-3481I&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2wb9glEWkllrQivebn5ckhE&amp;index=35\" target=\"_blank\">Am-5</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=onvxL8mP55o&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2xD07bSIbYB093JOYYYcpd-&amp;index=5\" target=\"_blank\">Op114-4</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wDC6ngDtOxA&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yEr5d3JjfNgMAzKeyN8Kwy&amp;index=22\" target=\"_blank\">Et2</a></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3SPqmWv91g&amp;list=PL5rvIaZKXz2yLEe7vOhlm56wR-La9kk9N&amp;index=17\" target=\"_blank\">Op30-10</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com