>1 2 b3 4 5 b6 b7</font></font> (C D Eb F G Ab Bb) - </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 2 1 2 2 1 2 2\n\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">Phrygian scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"> 1 b2 b3 4 5 b6 b7</font></font> (C Db Eb F G Ab Bb) -   </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 1 2 2 2 1 2 2\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n<span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">Locrian scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"> 1 b2 b3 4 b5 b6 b7</font></font> (C Db Eb F Gb Ab Bb) -  </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 1 2 2 1 2 2 2\n\n(These are in &quot;brightest&quot; to &quot;darkest&quot; order)\n\n\n\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">Harmonic minor scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"> 1 2 b3 4 5 b6 7</font></font> (C D Eb F G Ab B) - </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><strong>0 2 1 2 2 1 3 1 </strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"> \n\nMelodic minor scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"> 1 2 b3 4 5 6 7</font></font> (C D Eb F G A B) -    </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 2 1 2 2 2 2 1 - <em>while descending it&#39;s just same as Minor scale</em>\n\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">\nMinor pentatonic scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 1 b3 4 5 b7</font></font> (C Eb F G Bb) -       </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 3 2 2 3 2</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\nMajor pentatonic scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 1 2 3 5 6</font></font> (C D E G A) -           </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 2 2 3 2 3\n\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n<span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">Blues scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"> 1 b3 4 b5 5 b7</font></font> (C Eb F Gb G Bb) -            </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 3 2 1 1 3 2\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\nWhole tone scale =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 1 2 3 #4 #5 b7</font></font> (C D E F# G# Bb) -       </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 2 2 2 2 2 2\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">\nWhole-Half Diminished =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 1 2 b3 4 b5 b6 6 7</font></font> (C D Eb F Gb Ab A B) - </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 2 1 2 1 2 1 2 1\n</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#6d6d6d\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:300\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">\nHalf-Whole Diminished =<font color=\"#179cd8\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 1 b2 b3 3 b5 5 6 b7</font></font> (C Db Eb E F# G A Bb) - </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal;\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:300;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span style=\"orphans:2;\"><span style=\"text-transform:none;\"><span style=\"widows:2;\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>0 1 2 1 2 1 2 1 2</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></pre>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h1 id=\"music-youtube\">Chords:</h1>\n\n<p>Major Chord Shapes: (Root&nbsp;&mdash; <strong>3 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 3<sup>rd</sup> &mdash; <strong>2 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 5<sup>th</sup>)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Minor Chord Shapes: (Root&nbsp;&mdash; <strong>2 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 3<sup>rd</sup> &mdash; <strong>3 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 5<sup>th</sup>)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Dominant 7<sup>th</sup> Chord Shapes: (Root&nbsp;&mdash; <strong>3 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 3<sup>rd</sup> &mdash; <strong>2 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 5<sup>th</sup> &mdash; <strong>2 steps</strong> gap - flat 7<sup>th</sup> )</p>\n\n<p>For Maj7th it will be 7th instead of flat-7th</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Augmented Chord Shapes: (Root&nbsp;&mdash; <strong>3 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 3<sup>rd</sup> &mdash; <strong>3 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 5<sup>th</sup> sharp)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Diminished Chord Shapes: (Root&nbsp;&mdash; <strong>2 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 3<sup>rd</sup> flat &mdash; <strong>2 steps</strong> gap - Perfect 5<sup>th</sup> flat)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Triads:</p>\n\n<p>On 3-higher-strings: Inversions: A-shape (first inversion), E-shape (second inversion), D-shape (third inversion)</p>\n\n<p><u>Key of Am:</u></p>\n\n<p>Am -&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Dm -&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Em -&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Chords that go well together:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Primary - Am, Dm, E, E7&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Secondary - C, B7, A7</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chord Progressions:</strong></p>\n\n<p>1 5 4 1 4 6 2 3 2 6 ...</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>4, 5, 7 to create tension; 2, 3, 6 slow down tension; 1/8 to release..</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Circle of Fifths:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/circle-of-fifths-zapista-ou.jpeg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 500px;\" /></p>\n\n<hr />\n<h2>Key Signatures</h2>\n\n<p>Order of sharps: F&nbsp; &nbsp;C&nbsp; &nbsp;G&nbsp; &nbsp;D&nbsp; &nbsp;A&nbsp; &nbsp;E&nbsp; &nbsp;B</p>\n\n<p>Order of flats:&nbsp; &nbsp; B&nbsp; &nbsp;E&nbsp; &nbsp;A&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; D&nbsp; &nbsp;G&nbsp; C&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;F</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The name of any flat key is the second last flat in key signature (F major has only one flat though).&nbsp;So, the key signatures based on number of sharps: B E A D G C.</p>\n\n<p>The name of sharp key is last sharp in key signature + 1 half-step (or semi-tone). So, the key signatures based on number of sharps: G D A E B F C</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>X -major is same as X#-major key except for C (because C has no sharp) and F (because F has only one flat).</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Time Signatures:</h3>\n\n<p>E.g. 3-4 time signature means 3 4-th (quartets) notes in one measure. The pieces normally would start with less than 3 (in the first measure) though! Anything that sums up to this number would work. Rests are also counted.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.classicalguitarshed.com/free-guitar-sheet-music/\">Free Sheet/Tab Music</a>&nbsp;- <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5l6piMQ6hw&amp;list=PLE32FpNcePwOTsp1DxBozAvdZX2xnkeoX&amp;index=1\" target=\"_blank\">Course Videos</a>,&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTDhXdfeHZI&amp;list=PLS09nFAGbaWPuDpNlUtjTpW3b4Fo-hEO4\" target=\"_blank\">Robert Luhn</a></li>